The image shows a man (finnygainz) taking a selfie in what appears to be a gym locker room. He is wearing a blue t-shirt, and the background includes lockers. His caption is "#fitnessjourney progress".
The image shows a close-up of a sandwich made with whole wheat bread, boiled eggs, Swiss cheese, and tomatoes. The caption mentions "low fat gainz right here."
The image shows a person outdoors, drinking from a can. There is an ATV in the background, and the person is wearing a tank top with a logo. The TikTok logo is also visible.
The image shows a man wearing a mask with a New York Yankees logo, doing air squats in a gym. The post caption mentions "practicing some air squats to perfect my squat form".
The image is a post from Instagram user "finnygainz" advertising white Under Armour t-shirts for sale. The post caption encourages viewers to send offers.
